Package frc.discordslackbot.commands

Class TurnCommand

java.lang.Object
frc.discordslackbot.commands.AbstractCommand
frc.discordslackbot.commands.TurnCommand
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class TurnCommand
extends AbstractCommand
This very nice command will make the robot drive! Similar to a point-to-point auton, this command does not steer, it just drives in a straight line and it is up to the user to command turns and remain clear of obstacles
